OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,FA historian from County Durham who
OL,7,Fbecame a social media sensation for
OL,8,Fher witty take on social history on
OL,9,FTikTok, has been named in this year's
OL,10,FForbes 30 under 30, Europe, Media and
OL,11,FMarketing list.
OL,13,FKatie Kennedy, 26, from Chester-le-
OL,14,FStreet, is known online as The History
OL,15,FGossip. Her one minute quirky TikTok
OL,16,Fvideos haul in more than 600,00
OL,17,Ffollowers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,FShe told ITV News Tyne Tees being
OL,7,Frecognised in this way has already
OL,8,Fstarted opening new doors. She said:
OL,9,F"I actually couldn't stop crying, it
OL,10,Fwas such a validating experience,
OL,11,Fbeing on the list and being on the
OL,12,Flist with so many huge people who are
OL,13,Fdoing so many amazing things."
OL,15,FInspired by Terry Deary's Horrible
OL,16,FHistories as a child, Katie said she
OL,17,Flikes to focus her videos more on
OL,18,Fsocial history rather than the
OL,19,Fpolitical, royal or military genres of
OL,20,Fthe past.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,FThe influencer said: "I remember what
OL,7,Fpeople like me used to do back then?
OL,8,FWould I have been a coal miner's wife,
OL,9,For chimney sweep? Social history, I
OL,10,Fpersonally find that the most
OL,11,Finteresting, because I find that
OL,12,Frelatable. I like to do a lot of
OL,13,Fdifferent topics, even stuff that are
OL,14,Fhuman interest stories, like what
OL,15,Fpeople used before toilet roll, you
OL,16,Fdon't get taught that at school."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
