OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,FDespite studying for a Masters at
OL,7,FOxford, hosting TV shows, a podcast
OL,8,Fand publishing her first book, she
OL,9,Fsays she suffers from imposter
OL,10,Fsyndrome.
OL,12,FKatie explained: "In my head all the
OL,13,Ftime I'm like do I deserve to be here?
OL,14,FAm I going to be taken seriously,
OL,15,Fbecause of the way I talk about
OL,16,Fhistory?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,F"I talk about it in a very light
OL,7,Fhearted and fun way, and I like to
OL,8,Ftake the mickey a little bit, because
OL,9,Fhistory is fun at the end of the day;
OL,10,Fit's just scandals and seeing what
OL,11,Fpeople were doing back then and all of
OL,12,Fthe stuff they got up to, and who was
OL,13,Fgetting with who."
OL,15,FShe goes by the North East mantra of
OL,16,F'shy bairns get nowt' as she pushes
OL,17,Fherself out of her comfort zone. By
OL,18,Fdoing so she tries to engage audiences
OL,19,Fby making history more accessible to
OL,20,Fthe younger generations, using the
OL,21,Fsocial media platforms.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1780326668
OL,3,CTikTok Historian makes Forbes 30 under
OL,4,C30 list
OL,6,FShe added: "They're going to be on
OL,7,Fyour video for about three seconds,
OL,8,Fand if they don't care they're going
OL,9,Fto scroll away, so I need to try and
OL,10,Fmake it engaging for a TikTok
OL,11,Fgeneration and a platform that, they
OL,12,Fmight be interested in history, but
OL,13,Fthey might not have studied it or they
OL,14,Fmight not really care that much, so
OL,15,Fit's sort of like keeping people
OL,16,Fengaged."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
